      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills transportation option. The exterior has several cosmetic imperfections, including some noticeable paint chips on the front bumper and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining consistent with regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives fine, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape.",
